    Configuration.java Configuration creates and stores the user's preferences as to theme and tile visibility.

    This class is used to refresh Team 14's tokens when they expire

    Class to display the settings menu User can hide/remove tiles and re-display them User can also change colour of themes
    TestDataDaily
    TestDataDaily provides fake test data for other coders to use while testing without being involved with API.dat
    TestHeartRate
    Class to test whether the user's heart rate is within the specified zones
